{"tid":1559521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日聽到好多新口號 想問下有啲乜嘢","createTime":"2019-09-11T00:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:33:47.000Z","uid":301332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21352a85139c82bfa3b656bba7abe516d0bbd689","tid":1559521,"uid":301332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"琴日行過將軍澳先聽到原來有活動，於是落去同大家一齊嗌，但係我發現有好多新口號係之前遊行嗰啲冇聽過。<br />\n<br />\n例如我成日以為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「黑警」</span></span>係對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「還眼」</span></span>，但琴日大家係叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「死全家」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有一句我聽唔到上一句係乜嘢，總之回番嗰句係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「當差正仆街」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有無人可以介紹返新口號s?"},{"pid":"e316ee0909e3d8150f4cb61a7e84d4fae68ccc48","tid":1559521,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"eda4c087955897d48435abd90b81b523f0f47fb7","tid":1559521,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差"},{"pid":"01865395d131c0893498f1106686fa50d7e47afa","tid":1559521,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫左好耐"}]}